Clyde Allison aka ( William Henley Knowles ) James Bond parody For Your Sighs Only 1966 Ember Library

This book has all the usual William Knowles/Clyde Allison madness.  The story starts with a nude Alpine ski chase, which has to be my all time favorite opening to a novel.  The language in the book is hysterically overblown and the sex scenes are just intended to be silly.  There is a 4-5 page passage towards the beginning of the book where Agent 0008, Trevor Anderson, just deals with his female co-agents breasts.  Knowles had his own style in the vein of Terry Southern and some of the other post-beat writers of the ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã‹Å“60s, and it was really quite funny.

